<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:20:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>斯里兰卡未能与债券持有人就重组条款达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-fails-agree-restructuring-terms-with-bondholders-2024-04-16/</link><description>斯里兰卡政府周二表示，未能与其债券持有人就约 120 亿美元债务的重组达成协议，这使得该国满足国际货币基金组织计划要求的计划变得更加复杂。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-fails-agree-restructuring-terms-with-bondholders-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度推迟批准 Paytm 对其支付部门的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-defers-approval-paytms-investment-its-payments-arm-sources-say-2024-04-16/</link><description>据三名政府官员和路透社看到的一份文件称，印度推迟批准 Paytm 对其 Paytm 支付服务部门 5 亿卢比（600 万美元）的投资，部分原因是担心中国在母公司持股。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-defers-approval-paytms-investment-its-payments-arm-sources-say-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>德国肖尔茨：我要求中国习近平向俄罗斯施压，要求其停止战争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-i-asked-chinas-xi-pressure-russia-stop-war-2024-04-16/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周二表示，他已要求中国国家主席习近平对俄罗斯施加影响，以结束乌克兰战争，并补充说，两位领导人都拒绝袭击核设施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-i-asked-chinas-xi-pressure-russia-stop-war-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>德国财长肖尔茨：不会与中国脱钩，但需要在结构性问题上取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-no-decoupling-china-need-progress-structural-issues-2024-04-16/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周二表示，德国不想与中国“脱钩”，但呼吁在结构性问题上取得进展并提高合作质量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germanys-scholz-no-decoupling-china-need-progress-structural-issues-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，盛宝银行正在探索包括出售在内的战略选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/saxo-bank-explores-strategic-options-including-sale-sources-say-2024-04-16/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，在与一家空白支票公司的合并谈判破裂 18 个月后，丹麦盛宝银行正在考虑出售的可能性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/saxo-bank-explores-strategic-options-including-sale-sources-say-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：炙手可热的零售数据推动美国经济和美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-16/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>英特尔将为中国推出两款功能有所缩减的AI芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-launch-two-ai-chips-china-with-reduced-capabilities-2024-04-16/</link><description>英特尔将向中国市场推出两款功能有所降低的人工智能芯片，以遵守美国的出口管制和制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-launch-two-ai-chips-china-with-reduced-capabilities-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易主管戴秉国表示正在“认真研究”与中国打交道的工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-trade-chief-tai-says-taking-serious-look-tools-deal-with-china-2024-04-16/</link><description>美国贸易代表凯瑟琳·戴将于周二告诉议员，拜登政府正在“认真研究”美国的贸易防御工具，以应对中国贸易和经济政策构成的威胁，包括审查特朗普时代对中国进口产品征收的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-trade-chief-tai-says-taking-serious-look-tools-deal-with-china-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉全球裁员包括主要市场美国和中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-global-job-cuts-include-leading-markets-us-china-2024-04-16/</link><description>五位知情人士透露，特斯拉的全球裁员计划包括在美国和中国这两个汽车制造商最大的销售、技术和工程市场裁员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-global-job-cuts-include-leading-markets-us-china-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国囤积美元和人民币贬值的恶性循环</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinas-cycle-dollar-hoarding-weakening-yuan-gets-vicious-2024-04-16/</link><description>中国企业囤积美元是因为他们预计本国货币会贬值，而这反过来又加剧了人民币因股市波动和世界第二大经济体增长乏力而贬值。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinas-cycle-dollar-hoarding-weakening-yuan-gets-vicious-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>本田将于 2027 年在中国推出下一代电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-launch-next-generation-evs-china-by-2027-2024-04-16/</link><description>日本本田汽车公司周二表示，计划到 2027 年在中国推出六款以 Ye 为品牌的下一代电动汽车 (EV) 车型。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:00:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-launch-next-generation-evs-china-by-2027-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲对冲基金第一季度受益于日本反弹和中国复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-funds-benefit-q1-japan-rally-recovery-china-2024-04-16/</link><description>专注于亚洲的对冲基金在 2024 年第一季度表现强劲，受益于日本股市的长期上涨、中国股市的初步好转以及人工智能 (AI) 股票的繁荣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-funds-benefit-q1-japan-rally-recovery-china-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国驻联合国特使敦促俄罗斯和中国不要“奖励”朝鲜的不良行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-un-urges-russia-china-not-reward-north-koreas-bad-behaviour-2024-04-16/</link><description>美国驻联合国大使周二敦促俄罗斯和中国改弦易辙，停止奖励朝鲜的不良行为并保护其免受因武器计划而逃避制裁的活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-un-urges-russia-china-not-reward-north-koreas-bad-behaviour-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，特斯拉全球裁员对中国销售团队造成打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-global-job-cuts-hit-china-sales-team-sources-say-2024-04-16/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，特斯拉的全球裁员计划正在影响中国，这是该汽车制造商继美国之后的最大市场，影响到包括销售在内的团队员工。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-global-job-cuts-hit-china-sales-team-sources-say-2024-04-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国郑州要求国有企业购买二手房以减少新房库存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-city-zhengzhou-tells-state-owned-company-buy-second-hand-homes-reduce-2024-04-16/</link><description>中国中部城市郑州已要求居民将二手房出售给当地国有公司，然后购买新房，以减少新房库存并提振当地房地产业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-city-zhengzhou-tells-state-owned-company-buy-second-hand-homes-reduce-2024-04-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>